description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Berry Sherbet
-Mango Panna Cotta & Jelly
-Red Velvet Cake
-Panna Cotta with Berry Sauce
-Chocolate & Cream with Strawberry 
-Petit Gateau & Ice Cream
-Strawberry Tiramisu with Mascarpone
-Pumpkin Cupcake
-Chocolate Cake
-Raspberry Dessert
name: Sweets Wonderland
